  "title": "Financial Service Consultant",
  "description": "<p><strong>Candidates from different experience are welcome! </strong><br /><strong>Good remuneration - allowance + commission </strong><br /><strong>Yearly incentive trips </strong><br /><strong>Career progression </strong><br /><br />The organization is recognized for its stable market presence and focus on long-term client success through innovative financial strategies.</p><p>As a Financial Consultant, you will deliver integrated financial advice and bespoke investment solutions to help clients achieve their long-term wealth objectives.</p><ul><li><p>Provide holistic financial planning encompassing legacy, estate planning, and asset allocation.</p></li><li><p>Develop and maintain strong business relationships with a diverse portfolio of local and international clients.</p></li><li><p>Conduct market research to identify and capitalize on new business opportunities.</p></li><li><p>Deliver customized investment strategies and portfolio management solutions.</p></li><li><p>Collaborate with cross-functional teams to ensure high-quality service delivery across multiple work environments.</p></li></ul><p>skills and experience required.</p><p><ul><li>Degree or Diploma in any discipline with a strong willingness to learn and adapt.<br />Exceptional interpersonal skills with the ability to communicate effectively across various client segments.<br />Self-motivated individual with strong organizational skills and a passion for financial advisory<br /></li></ul></p><p>Please click on the 'apply' button to apply online. <br />(EA: 94C3609/ R21103354)</p>",
